     "skill_arcana"),
    ("Perception (DEF stat): Noticing hidden objects, detecting ambushes, spotting subtle clues.",
     "skill_perception"),
    ("Stealth (MOV stat): Moving silently, hiding in shadows, avoiding detection by guards or monsters.",
